# MAROKI
## _A great WordPress boilerplate developers_

A minimalist rich WordPress boilerplate repository provides a solid foundation for any type of WordPress project.

## Features

- SCSS to CSS conversion
- Watching\Compiling\Minifying javascript files
- Vue.js and Bootstrap support
- Translation support
- Template support

## Tech

MAROKI uses a number of open source projects to work properly:

- [Vue.js](#) - HTML enhanced for web apps!
- [Bootstrap](#) - awesome web-based text editor
- [Gulp](#) - Markdown parser done right. Fast and easy to extend.

## Installation

MAROKI requires [Node.js](https://nodejs.org/) v10+ to run.

```sh
git clone git@github.com:naycho334/wordpress-plugin-boilerplate.git
cd wordpress-plugin-boilerplate
npm i
```

#### Watch SCSS

For watching scss:

```sh
gulp watchscss
```
#### Compile JS

For compiling js:

```sh
gulp compilejs
```
#### Compress plugin zip file

For compressing plugin zip file:

```sh
gulp pack
```


